divs: Sighting DetailsA woman driving along a lakeshore observed a domed silvery disc, 60 feet indiameter, with 6-12 pulsating red lights around the rim that created an aura.After hovering initially, the object roughly paced the auto from near the shore,surging and slowing about twice per second. It also ascended quickly and nearlyvertically from 100 to 1,000 feet above the water, descended at a 45-degreeangle, and finally moved out of viewing range.
Summary: Domed disc paced auto, then moved away.
